trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectEvents.DeploymentStarted" /> and <see cref="E:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectEvents.DeploymentCompleted" /> events.
trans-unit.target: 提供有关 <see cref="E:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectEvents.DeploymentStarted" /> 和 <see cref="E:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectEvents.DeploymentCompleted" /> 事件的数据。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectEvents.DeploymentStarted> and <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectEvents.DeploymentCompleted> events are raised when a SharePoint project is deployed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectEvents.DeploymentStarted>和<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectEvents.DeploymentCompleted>部署 SharePoint 项目时将引发事件。

trans-unit.source: For more information about handling these events, see [How to: Run Code When a SharePoint Project is Deployed or Retracted](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-run-code-when-a-sharepoint-project-is-deployed-or-retracted.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关处理这些事件的详细信息，请参阅[如何： 运行代码 SharePoint 项目时是部署或收回](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-run-code-when-a-sharepoint-project-is-deployed-or-retracted.md)。
